node.text: You rock our world @hudsonsheaffer 🤍 how did Hendrix and I get so lucky?! We love you more than words could ever express. You are our balance, our inspiration, problem solver, spider exterminator, top shelf reacher, our protector, our adventure guide, our best friend, our light, and by far the best baby daddy a gal could ever dream of, and so so so much more. I’m so happy I get to grow old with you and beat you at every card game we play 😉 Happy Birthday baby, here’s to 32.

node.text: Wishing my beautiful best friend, MySpace #1, shoulder to cry on, high school dance date, Sidekick > BlackBerry queen, crazy intelligent, life of the party, hot Cheeto loving, LAWYER, sister, and the best Ninang (Godmother,) the most wonderful of birthdays! The world does not deserve you. You are both gentle and strong and I am always in awe of what you accomplish. Thank you for gracing our lives. We love you SO MUCH! #17yearsoffriendship #soulsister 🌸

node.text: Today is #WorldHumanitarianDay. Please support @thehalotrust and the work they've been doing in Afghanistan for the last 33 years clearing over 850,000 landmines and other explosive hazards to make the streets safe for children and families. The 2,500 Afghanis they employ need our help now more than ever. #HaloTrust #Afghanistan 🙏

node.text: Beyond excited to announce this one. It has been an absolute treat playing Ms. Aruba-Tate…you’re going to adore her 💗 So honored to be included in such a wonderful cast. And I always love being directed by the talented @elissa_down #ivyandbean #msarubatate
